Package PayrollProcessing

Class Management

java.lang.Object
PayrollProcessing.Employee
PayrollProcessing.Fulltime
PayrollProcessing.Management
public class Management
extends Fulltime
Management class implements objects that inherit properties of the Fulltime class. Includes data and operations specific to Fulltime Employees with management roles.
Author:
Connie Chen, Tiffany Lee
